# t-ron — MCP security monitor (Cyrius port)
#
# 2.1.x — modernization arc. 2.1.0 lands the cyrius 5.10.34 floor
# and swaps the per-module libro/bote include sets for the single
# dist/<crate>.cyr bundles (libro 2.6.2 / bote 2.7.1). 2.1.x is
# reserved for the remaining first-party-floor items — see
# docs/development/roadmap.md.

